com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.kms

Interface ProvidersTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Providers
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProvidersStub

    public interface ProvidersTypes
    The Providers interface provides methods to create, update and delete Key Providers that handoff to key servers. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.0.0.
